---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 329
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=On ‘Karma’ and ‘Karma Yoga’
By: Asvaghosha
Commentary: Simply because whatever has a beginning must have an end.
---
There is ever to living creatures fear from death, and they with all
their efforts seek to be born again; where there is action, there must
inevitably be death.
